{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f69ba562-a9b9-4ab3-98bd-758cd66a8c16", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f69ba562-a9b9-4ab3-98bd-758cd66a8c16@1.pkg/1772597676043/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597676938", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f69ba562-a9b9-4ab3-98bd-758cd66a8c16@1.pkg/1772597676043/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597676938"}, "identifier": "f69ba562-a9b9-4ab3-98bd-758cd66a8c16", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查孝亲敬长的内涵。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：意思是长辈年老时，要常常关心他们的冷暖，早晚问候日常作息，直接体现了对长辈的关心和照料，蕴含着孝亲敬长的内涵。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：强调和朋友交往要讲诚信，做事要凭良心，与孝亲敬长无关。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：说的是多读书能积累知识，让写作更顺畅，讲的是学习的道理。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：体现的是为人处世要宽厚、待人要真诚，属于待人之道。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>故选为A</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）孝亲敬长是记挂父母的冷暖，是耐心听他们唠叨，是把日常陪伴藏进柴米油盐的温暖里。下列古语蕴含&ldquo;孝亲敬长&rdquo;精神内涵的是（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）孝亲敬长是记挂父母的冷暖，是耐心听他们唠叨，是把日常陪伴藏进柴米油盐的温暖里。下列古语蕴含“孝亲敬长”精神内涵的是（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "exam